strings:
<voice_0x01000B0B><se_high>Jessica: So that's how you met. But what happened to
all the laughter, thrills, and tears?
<voice_0x01000B0D><se_low>Yangus: This is the best bit! I 'aven't told ya about 'ow the guv 'elped me go straight...

<voice_0x01000B0E><se_high>Jessica: Whatever. You can tell me all about it later.
Right now, I need some fresh air.
<voice_0x01000B0F><se_low>Yangus: I shoulda known a bird wouldn't get a story like ours, guv.
<voice_0x01000B10><se_low>Yangus: Still, no skin off my nose.
